Package net.nicoulaj.maven.plugins.checksum.mojo

Implementations of Mojo for maven-checksum-plugin.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ArtifactsMojo Compute project artifacts checksum digests and store them in individual files and/or a summary file.
DependenciesMojo Compute project dependencies checksum digests and store them in a summary file.
FileMojo Compute specified file checksum digest for all supported checksum algorithms.
FilesMojo Compute specified files checksum digests and store them in individual files and/or a summary file.
HelpMojo Display help information on maven-checksum-plugin.
